research_municipality_step.notes: North Richland Hills operates under a Council-Manager form of government. The Mayor and seven Council Members are elected at-large, meaning there are no geographic districts for council places. There was a minor discrepancy for Place 2, where one source listed an 'Associate Mayor Pro Tem' with a different name, but multiple official city sources consistently list Brianne Goetz as the Council Member for Place 2. The full name for Matt Blake (Place 4) was found as Richard Matthew Blake.
